nodes.text: Good morning. I have a conflict; because of today weather I had to cancel an appointment at the Org2 dental clinic and it been rescheduled to MM/DD/YYYY at 1:00 PM. I also scheduled to meet with Dr. Person1 at  1:15 that day. Can we reschedule my appointment with Dr. Person1? I really have to make this appointment with my Org2 dentist and the MM/DD/YYYY date is the earliest date available. (Earlier that day, perhaps?)
